tudy.</p> <p>High-achieving students can enrol in the Bachelor of Philosophy (Honours) program.</p> <p style="font-weight: bold;">Study Commerce online with Australia’s #1 Business School*</p> <p>Download your free course brochure to learn more about UC❛s online Bachelor of Commerce (Business Economics).</p> <p style="font-size: smaller;">*#1 Business School in Australia for Career Impact (AFR BOSS, 2023).</p> <p><a class="adobe-analytics" href="https://www.canberra.edu.au/future-students/study-at-uc/about-our-courses/bachelor-of-business" style="background: #006C91;color: #fff;display: inline-block;padding: 12px 20px;font-weight: bold;position: relative;border-radius: 25px;line-height: 100%;text-decoration: none;">Download your free course brochure</a></p> <p> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div>',
